	<Title>
		Quit smoking: Focus on today
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;When you&apos;re trying to quit smoking, don&apos;t get too caught up by what&apos;s down the road. Don&apos;t worry about next week or next month, since that may become overwhelming. Focus only on today. Every hour without a cigarette brings you one step closer to quitting for good and freedom from an unhealthy, expensive habit.&lt;/p&gt;
